Gloria Dawn (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gloria_Dawn_(actor) 0 Gloria Dawn (February 26, 1929 – April 2, 1978) was an Australian female actor and singer. She was one of Australia's leading stage stars in the 1960s and 1970s. Gloria_Dawn ( February_26_,_1929 – April_2_,_1978 ) was an_Australian_female_actor_and_singer .
